{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","blocks":{"heading":{"type":"text","name":"Title","settings":{"text":"<h1>Default Page<\/h1>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"center","type_preset":"h2","font":"var(--font-primary--family)","font_size":"","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"page-content":{"type":"page-content","disabled":true,"settings":{},"blocks":{}},"text_NKEG7g":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Insert Text Here<\/p>","width":"100%","max_width":"none","alignment":"center","type_preset":"h5","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["heading","page-content","text_NKEG7g"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"content_direction":"column","gap":32,"color_scheme":"","padding-block-start":40,"padding-block-end":40}},"section_V9LqjP":{"type":"section","blocks":{"text_UtTccc":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h3>Artwork Submissions for Custom Playmats  — FAQ<\/h3>","width":"100%","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"h3","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"accordion_ykRG8n":{"type":"accordion","name":"t:names.accordion","settings":{"icon":"caret","dividers":true,"type_preset":"h5","inherit_color_scheme":true,"color_scheme":"","border":"none","border_width":1,"border_opacity":100,"border_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{"accordion_row_a7TGaf":{"type":"_accordion-row","settings":{"heading":"What are the artwork requirements for custom playmats?","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","width":20},"blocks":{"text_VbVx9t":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>We support two standard sizes:<\/p><ul><li><strong>24\" x 14\"<\/strong> — total canvas size with bleed: <strong>24.5\" x 14.5\"<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>28\" x 14\"<\/strong> — total canvas size with bleed: <strong>28.5\" x 14.5\"<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><p>Each requires <strong>0.25\" bleed<\/strong> on all sides. Please ensure your background art extends to the full canvas size.<\/p>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_VbVx9t"]},"accordion_row_3KEpgb":{"type":"_accordion-row","settings":{"heading":"What is the safe zone and why does it matter?","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","width":20},"blocks":{"text_izPyNy":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>The <strong>safe zone<\/strong> protects your key design elements from being trimmed or obscured during production.<\/p><ul><li>Keep all important content (text, logos, faces, focal points) at least <strong>1\" inside<\/strong> the final trim size.<\/li><li>Avoid placing anything critical near the edges — even if it looks centered digitally, trimming can vary slightly.<\/li><\/ul>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_izPyNy"]},"accordion_row_MBwxXV":{"type":"_accordion-row","name":"t:names.accordion_dash_row","settings":{"heading":"When will I get my What resolution should my artwork be?","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","width":20},"blocks":{"text_gnJKLy":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>We require high-resolution files to ensure crisp, vibrant prints:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Minimum<\/strong>: 600 DPI<\/li><li><strong>Maximum<\/strong>: 1200 DPI<\/li><\/ul><p>Lower resolutions may result in blurry or pixelated output.<\/p>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_gnJKLy"]},"accordion_row_W6wXmh":{"type":"_accordion-row","name":"t:names.accordion_dash_row","settings":{"heading":"What file formats do you accept?","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","width":20},"blocks":{"text_bDYdnQ":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>We accept the following <strong>flat image formats<\/strong> only:<\/p><ul><li><strong>JPG<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>PNG<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>TIFF<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><p>Please do <strong>not<\/strong> submit files with layers, transparency, or alpha channels. Flatten your artwork before exporting.<\/p>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_bDYdnQ"]},"accordion_row_qGPyHh":{"type":"_accordion-row","name":"t:names.accordion_dash_row","settings":{"heading":"What color profile should I use?","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","width":20},"blocks":{"text_UBmyrN":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Use <strong>Adobe RGB (1998)<\/strong> for optimal vibrancy in dye sublimation printing.<\/p><ul><li>Do <strong>not<\/strong> use sRGB or CMYK — these may result in dull or inaccurate colors.<\/li><li>Make sure your file is properly tagged with the Adobe RGB profile before submitting.<\/li><\/ul>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_UBmyrN"]},"accordion_row_MAjjwp":{"type":"_accordion-row","name":"t:names.accordion_row","settings":{"heading":"What should I avoid when preparing my artwork?","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","width":20},"blocks":{"text_NeJW4F":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>To ensure your design prints correctly, avoid:<\/p><ul><li>Submitting files below 600 DPI<\/li><li>Using sRGB or CMYK color profiles<\/li><li>Including layers, transparency, or alpha channels<\/li><li>Placing key content too close to the edge<\/li><li>Forgetting to extend the background art to the bleed area<\/li><\/ul>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_NeJW4F"]},"accordion_row_RKfAYj":{"type":"_accordion-row","name":"t:names.accordion_row","settings":{"heading":"Is there a checklist I can follow before submitting?","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","width":20},"blocks":{"text_b7wxy7":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Absolutely. Here’s a quick checklist:<\/p><ul><li>[  ] Final size is 24\" x 14\" or 28\" x 14\"<\/li><li>[  ] Canvas includes 0.25\" bleed on all sides<\/li><li>[  ] Resolution is between 600–1200 DPI<\/li><li>[  ] File format is JPG, PNG, or TIFF<\/li><li>[  ] Color profile is Adobe RGB (1998)<\/li><li>[  ] Image is flattened (no layers or transparency)<\/li><li>[  ] Critical content is at least 1\" from trim edges<\/li><li>[  ] Background art extends futhe lly to bleed edge<\/li><\/ul>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_b7wxy7"]}},"block_order":["accordion_row_a7TGaf","accordion_row_3KEpgb","accordion_row_MBwxXV","accordion_row_W6wXmh","accordion_row_qGPyHh","accordion_row_MAjjwp","accordion_row_RKfAYj"]}},"block_order":["text_UtTccc","accordion_ykRG8n"],"name":"t:names.faq_section","settings":{"content_direction":"column","vertical_on_